@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title US-09 Generate Report: current implementation

actor Developer
participant "<u>entry scripts/tests</u>" as TS
participant "<u>logger/stdout/file io</u>" as OUT

Developer -> TS: run cartpole_brain_training.py / demo_driver.py / pytest
activate TS
TS -> OUT: print metrics, step logs, train/test summaries
OUT --> Developer: console text + optional saved artifacts

note over TS
No standalone ReportGenerator class exists.
Reporting is emitted by training/testing flows and log output.
end note

deactivate TS
@enduml
